<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[437, 165, 561, 183]]<|/det|>
## 1. ALGEBRA

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[79, 197, 240, 214]]<|/det|>
Quadratic Equation

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[116, 227, 384, 246]]<|/det|>
For the equation \(ax^{2} + bx + c = 0\),

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[420, 246, 584, 280]]<|/det|>
\[x = \frac{-b\pm\sqrt{b^{2} - 4ac}}{2a}.\]

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[79, 313, 230, 330]]<|/det|>
Binomial Theorem

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[243, 336, 754, 373]]<|/det|>
\[(a + b)^{n} = a^{n} + \binom{n}{1} a^{n - 1} b + \binom{n}{2} a^{n - 2} b^{2} + \ldots +\binom{n}{r} a^{n - r} b^{r} + \ldots +b^{n},\]

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[116, 384, 500, 419]]<|/det|>
where \(n\) is a positive integer and \(\binom{n}{r} = \frac{n!}{(n-r)!r!}\).

<|ref|>sub_title<|/ref|><|det|>[[401, 482, 596, 500]]<|/det|>
## 2. TRIGONOMETRY

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[79, 515, 158, 532]]<|/det|>
Identities

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[421, 545, 574, 565]]<|/det|>
\[\sin^{2}A + \cos^{2}A = 1\]

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[421, 570, 574, 590]]<|/det|>
\[\sec^{2}A = 1 + \tan^{2}A\]

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[413, 594, 584, 615]]<|/det|>
\[\csc^{2}A = 1 + \cot^{2}A\]

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[79, 643, 242, 660]]<|/det|>
Formulae for \(\Delta ABC\)

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[406, 666, 591, 696]]<|/det|>
\[\frac{a}{\sin A} = \frac{b}{\sin B} = \frac{c}{\sin C}\]

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[403, 718, 593, 738]]<|/det|>
\[a^{2} = b^{2} + c^{2} - 2bc \cos A\]

<|ref|>equation<|/ref|><|det|>[[440, 745, 559, 774]]<|/det|>
\[\Delta = \frac{1}{2} bc \sin A\]
